- Bye, Cleo.

555
01:04:34,604 --> 01:04:36,538
See you next week,
Mrs. Dorston.

556
01:04:46,315 --> 01:04:48,283
So, what do we have next?

557
01:04:55,825 --> 01:04:58,555
Don?

558
01:05:06,669 --> 01:05:09,137
So, you're an animal psychic?

559
01:05:09,272 --> 01:05:12,207
